data.description: Lovely brick ranch on .75 of an acre just minutes from St. Clairsville and I-70. This conveniently located home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, a two car attached garage, a galley kitchen with corian countertops, oak cabinets and all the appliances. There are updated laminate floors and plenty of natural light in the living room which leads out to a covered rear deck with a lower level patio from the walk out basement. Fresh paint, updated flooring, New interior French drains 2021, 200 amp electrical panel and home re-wired 2021, Concrete driveway, connected to county sewer and water. There is truly nothing left to do here but move in and make this home your own.
